    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "What are your plans for distributing those `kernel.json` files? For now I created them with my editor. I assumed that they're just files that are in some repo and can be installed by `IPython kernelspec install`.\n\nBut this probably does not work, since commands differ between windows and unix. Also if you cannot use `~`, the user has to be directly coded into the `julia`'s `kernel.json`.\n\nSo the kernels themselves are supposed to dynamically create those files and install them?\n"
  },
